TopicTitle: Can Someone tell why my ksp is crashing?

Articles.Content:
Can Someone tell why my ksp is crashing? I play on 1.11.1, and its modded.

Here is my ksp log: http://www.mediafire.com/file/pb0ra5swnjy7vz0/KSP.log/file

I can see some oddities yes, but no crash in the log. Do you have a crash.dmp?  As well as some more information so we have something to work with to find out what causes your issue (see my signature)?

I didn't found that file
That is unfortunate, crash dump often reveals the cause of a crash. The log you provided abruptly stops, not giving much useful information. Hard to analyze without having more to work with.

You're at least missing the dependencies for FMRS (ClickThroughBlocker and ToolbarController), as well as the required KerbinSide Remastered for KSC Extended. You probably also want to update EVE to EVE Redux, compiled for KSP 1.9-1.11.x.

This should at least eliminate most issues I've found in your log, which honestly doesn't look too bad but may cause the game to crash anyway.
